  "texts": [
    "We use a blockchain-based FL framework to train and distribute a collaborative model.",
    "Also, FL is used to merge the weights of a model that has been trained locally.",
    "The global model is returned to the resources or organization once the locally learned model weights are aggregated.Ensuring the privacy of our data sources is paramount in our approach.",
    "Blockchain technology serves as a protective shield, preventing the leakage of sensitive information.",
    "Transactions on the blockchain ledger come in two categories: data sharing and retrieval transactions."
